2026-05-16T02:49:32.5049923Z 12    <!--
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5050202Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5050475Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5051206Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5051481Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5051805Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
