2026-05-16T02:49:32.5053833Z 21    <!--
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5054089Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5054230Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5054482Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5054715Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5054951Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5055179Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5055573Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5055816Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5056055Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5056274Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5056406Z 32    -->
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5056713Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5057400Z 33-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/build/intermediates/tmp/manifest/test/debug/tempFile2ProcessTestManifest16694608731013639820.xml:34:5-79
