2026-05-16T02:49:32.5071087Z 51    <!--
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5071346Z 52        Foreground service used to keep the Pomodoro countdown alive when
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5071596Z 53        the app is backgrounded. Without this, a viewModelScope coroutine
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5071822Z 54        is cancelled as soon as the user switches apps and the completion
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5072027Z 55        notification is never shown. The timer is declared as a
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5072287Z 56        mediaPlayback foreground service because Samsung One UI suppresses
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5072531Z 57        FOREGROUND_SERVICE_SPECIAL_USE notifications, preventing the
2026-05-16T02:49:32.5073017Z 58        ongoing countdown notification from appearing on those devices.
